/>\n屌你老母清潔工九千蚊<br />\n雙糧萬八蚊仲少過班富豪資產啦<br />\n弱撚智 樓主知唔知乜撚野叫做最？</blockquote><br />\n咁你又知<br />\n千億兆佢地係富豪？ 個iq題個人物係我設定既 佢地係唔係富豪幾時到你話事 叫得阿兆一定係有錢人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母臭系又係呢d撚樣係度開iq題<br />\n算啦 我其他嘢都唔講 淨係討論下對於與錯嘅問題<br />\n點解一定要係你果個答案先叫做啱呀<br />\n其他人答唔同答案 你就話9人錯<br />\n屌你老母臭系 人地個答案分分仲鐘合理過你啦on9<br />\n<br />\n睇死你呢d撚樣 老母一定係比狗屌<br />\n先生到你呢d半人半狗既畜生<br />\n如果比我知道你真人係邊個 出街一定打97你<br />\n得你個答案先叫啱呀?on撚9</blockquote><br />\nchilunsin IQ題post咁撚認真去嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1cd89137c6e7a42eaec60394cf2da231aa3f1a","tid":263982,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:04:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主高汁</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8848cf683234ff8e9631b3e601211dff1f3ce28","tid":263982,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"樓豬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢度啲人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734a6709b3d99bed323b52ac7547dd31b5b53311","tid":263982,"uid":77394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連登仔都係好人黎 唔想我死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我開估啦 ans係萬 因為萬「是」有「雙糧」</blockquote><br />\n「邵」（兆）氏有基金 tim wo</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"db61e590a9887731b88d560d0d1a2cc8411ecbf3","tid":263982,"uid":58699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:55:28.000Z","msg":"獅子 因為LION"},{"pid":"7b3f5d2b3b26a354ad1a062b7482feced717e265","tid":263982,"uid":66303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T20:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09a84e9d91eb8f982c8d3af39ba8b7a91655523","tid":263982,"uid":24519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T20:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主唔洗自殺，不過希望你全家生癌又死唔去吊住條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗咁呀 開post玩下姐大家 好過啲假膠iq題啦。關家人咩事喎 我希望連登仔健健康康 開開<span style=\"color: red;\">心心</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個有雙糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n樓主幾好人 唔好死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3e22f1db68a68c77875c218f8a75850cb37f45","tid":263982,"uid":79838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"改改題目囉<br />\n阿千 阿萬⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n返同一份工<br />\n邊個出最多錢糧<br />\n<br />\n會唔會無咁ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec06380412638e80713b4fbc68bed3fe3af3f53","tid":263982,"uid":42971,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:17:33.000Z","msg":"一個post見到嗮班on9仔小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝樓主幫大家釣嗮啲小學雞出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec44cfc820d9c7902203ff24efc65564cc97e4fa","tid":263982,"uid":99911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"兩邊冷靜少少先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n客觀少少睇條iq題 iq題的確係可以好天馬行空 好似上面位巴打提出嘅例子：花「識」溜冰咁<br />\n<br />\n但論高唔高質除左睇個答案之外 我地唔好忘記 條問題都好重要架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主一開始剩係打左「千 億 萬 兆 邊個最有錢」<br />\n而樓主開估嘅答案就係「萬」 個原因係「萬『是』有『雙糧』」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實真係可以好似呢條咁「咩植物最得閒？」答案係「葉」原因係「葉『得閒』」<br />\n雖然係咁無聊 玩食字<br />\n但你又唔會鬧佢出得差、戇鳩、低質等等<br />\n<br />\n樓主有食字 但有雙糧就代表最有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢點相信好多人都睇唔透<br />\n其實真係成立唔到「萬」係最有錢 係不合理<br />\n除非你話有句野叫「萬事最有錢」 咁好多人都會話你「好高汁啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n因此 呢條iq題真係出得唔係咁好<br />\n可能係個問題唔好 亦有可能係個答案或者原因唔好<br />\n<br />\n或者好似有其他巴打係上面提出一啲更好嘅問法 樓主若果一早咁問 應該可以避免巴打們嘅爭執<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主繼續努力 來日方長 係不久嘅將來出啲高質嘅iq題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6131af627cdb88a00c6f49dd803f05ad958b1016","tid":263982,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:29:44.000Z","msg":"多謝樓上果位巴打咁詳細既分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係上面都有講過我呢題出得唔太好 因為原本打算係問邊個最鐘意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}